oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Courting in Curlee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of courting couples at the Curlee Church of Christ in the Curlee Community. Pictured are John Harvey Simpson (1886-1963), Ethel Williams, Ora Lee Paschal Reed (1893-1969), Julie Youree, George E. Lassiter (1887-1957), Maude Williams, Sam C. Knox (1891-1964), Jessie Simpson Knox (1890-1950), Vernon L Reed (1891-1967), Clevie Lassiter, Tom Lassiter, Sallie Ivie, J. N., Nancy, and Annie Mae Lassiter.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Courtship; Couples
